7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Leonardo AI and Stable Diffusion share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Image To Image, Inpainting, Upscaling. On the other hand, Stable Diffusion uniquely offers Outpainting, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Leonardo AI holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Stable Diffusion scores 9/10 overall and 3/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Leonardo AI and Stable Diffusion offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Leonardo AI's free tier and Stable Diffusion's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
